# Google Maps Platform API key.
#
# Required APIs/settings on this key:
#   1. Enable "Maps JavaScript API" in the Google Cloud Console:
#      https://console.cloud.google.com/google/maps-apis/api-list
#   2. Confirm the project has access to 3D Maps (the `maps3d` library).
#      As of 2026 this ships via the alpha channel (`v=alpha`) of the
#      Maps JavaScript API bootstrap loader. See:
#      https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/javascript/3d/get-started
#   3. Restrict the key (HTTP referrers) to your local dev origin and any
#      deployed origins before using it anywhere but localhost.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in your real key there.
# `.env.local` is gitignored and is never committed.
VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=
